+  // Slice-once: build, per core, a module containing ONLY that core plus the
+  // device shell (tiles/buffers/locks/objectfifos/globals/runtime-sequence), and
+  // hand each worker its own small slice. Previously every worker parsed AND
+  // cloned the entire N-core module and the lowering then discarded the other
